        {
            "id": 6306111,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 費城半導體大漲3%，報7659.12點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間10日04:07，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲223.02點（或3%），暫報7659.12點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+0.93%</li><li>近 1 月：+0.83%</li><li>近 3 月：+8.39%</li><li>近 6 月：+31.82%</li><li>今年以來：+0.93%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)領漲。英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)上漲10.79%；科林研發(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LRCX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LRCX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LRCX-US</a>)上漲8.57%；艾司摩爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ASML:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ASML\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ASML-US</a>)上漲6.85%；應用材料(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMAT-US</a>)上漲6.64%；科磊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:KLAC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/KLAC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">KLAC-US</a>)上漲5.53%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，高通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QCOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QCOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QCOM-US</a>)下跌1.69%；安謀控股公司(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ARM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ARM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ARM-US</a>)下跌1.17%；凌雲邏輯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRUS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRUS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRUS-US</a>)下跌0.39%；超微半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMD-US</a>)下跌0.07%。</p></section></main>",
